Package: scPharm
Title: Identification of pharmacological subpopulations of single cells for precision medicine in cancers
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Peng", "Tian", email = "2131443@tongji.edu.cn",role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Jie", "Zheng", role= c("aut", "ctb"), email = "2210791@tongji.edu.cn"),
    person("Haiyun", "Wang", role= c("aut", "ctb"), email = "wanghaiyun@tongji.edu.cn"))
Description: scPharm is a computational framework tailored for scRNA-seq data, integrating pharmacogenomics profiles to uncover therapeutic heterogeneity within tumours at single-cell resolution.
    The tool not only prioritizes tailored drugs but also provides insight into combination therapy regimen and drug toxicity in cancers.
